  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I was wondering, what's going to happen when I come and tell my sister [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that I want to get married and things like that?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her husband came then from the-- from the war where they took him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came into the house, my husband and her husband from the same city, from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told me right away from which family he comes and who he is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's not married, and he's so and so, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then so we had already witness that I'm not marrying somebody who's got a wife, and then when I come back, we're going to find a wife with children or something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was always- A lot of people did it, and then they were sorry, because they had to separate later when they came back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went into the [NON-ENGLISH] they call it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like the city hall in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for three ruble, we got married, and we still lived with-- with them, together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a small room, and we couldn't-- so I decide, and I said to my husband, look, let's go out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he start working in a place where they used to bring corn to make flour.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they brought it from other provinces, and he went into work, [NON-ENGLISH], they used to call it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in Samarkand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we left them, and we went to where the train comes in, and I found one small room with a Uzbek woman, with a child, there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had my little room in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he used to work in the [NON-ENGLISH] for the-- there was a place that used to bring the--",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
